a-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWEkTz9T.jpg&h=94e80f79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a1d86c1fd9fccb135e77855fe56699be79e755a","tid":1538790,"uid":240950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:02:58.000Z","msg":"我都要喺隻手刻返  [布仇」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54571086ec05c7cadad6f6bcb429a34c779e84aa","tid":1538790,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"依家重有人叫中共做中央?<br />\n你估中共會放過新疆西藏咩<br />\n兩邊都傳聞死左好多人"},{"pid":"9522b1a958258a4c31c7fd48b7c7c5ea9afc983a","tid":1538790,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcgb58P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcgb58P.gif&h=4c045c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep8qq8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp8qq8P.gif&h=b74f62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 至今嚴重昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n袋住先 放風降溫<br />\n大追捕 清算 正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"7646805c919470e035a3c0cf63a585726adc2e6c","tid":1538790,"uid":240950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54571086ec05c7cadad6f6bcb429a34c779e84aa","tid":1538790,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"依家重有人叫中共做中央?<br />\n你估中共會放過新疆西藏咩<br />\n兩邊都傳聞死左好多人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"你想叫人做野   會唔會用仆街叫對方"},{"pid":"2f8be2cfd1e2b3c9d7156ea5f6c295e07a6a577c","tid":1538790,"uid":240950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"中共=仆街 <br />\n中央係書面禮貌稱呼"},{"pid":"ffcbe4cd07c0ab258dd9c748420ea536e5ebfdf8","tid":1538790,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:26:57.000Z","msg":"即時槍決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd09aefa094ff11f7696e8c2259c868d000aa366","tid":1538790,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:28:57.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"}]}